# Keep the published tarball free of build artifacts and stray binaries.
# (The `files` allowlist in package.json controls what's included; this
# trims unwanted files from within those allowed paths.)

# Native/compiled build outputs
*.lib
*.exe
*.dll
*.exp
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.obj
*.o
build/

# ...but DO ship the prebuilt addon + its bundled ICU runtime DLLs.
!prebuilds/**/*.node
!prebuilds/**/*.dll

# VCS / CI / dev noise that may live inside otherwise-shipped dirs
.github/
.git/
*.log
